{
  "title": "Tazulriulringane ki Ngudradrekay",
  "titleCh": "魯凱族的造林保林運動",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "「再造林」是日語借詞，是外來政權來到台灣後才有的。之前，沒有宣導如何保林造林的知識，後來，在耕作地上砍伐大量樹木，把土地開墾得光禿禿的，反而成為破壞水土的元兇。",
      "ab": "Kikay “wazulringi” amia Dridripungane ka vaga, amani sakelanga kay singikay badhanane mitaane ka suakay Tayvange, kaiana wakela ku wabulru ku luludane si atukucingalrane ki waduuku walredreke ku laangatu, makakalralringa ku tamualrane ku angatu ki tatuumaumane, kadrua ku tasuusuane ngualralrivadhane. Ai, amaninga ku matiaukuludru ku pakay ki kadaengane ku angutukadranane si ngilisiane ku kadalranane.",
      "order": "1",
