    {
      "chinese": "民國時代，推動山地造林運動，退伍老兵整批進入山林。但是，大量種植相思樹反而帶來最慘烈的破壞。",
      "ab": "Sakelanga kay Ciwkuku, lapazulringi kay sualringimukiwke ki kacalrisiane si kuapingi ka singikay Taireke, ai, wazulringi kay tatukulu, sisiziw amia dridripungane. Alakamani ku maadraadrawnga ku tualisi ki kadaengane ki kacalrisiane kikay tatukulu.",
